                     </persName>
                  , one bank note value 300l. one other bank note, value 100l. one other bank note, value 30l. and three other bank notes, each of the value of 20l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17960217-9-victim126" type="victimName">
                     Ann 
                     Salt
                  <interp inst="t17960217-9-victim126" type="surname" value="Salt"></interp>
