               GUILTY Of stealing the property
            </rs>, (Aged 36.) Dew. <rs id="t17960217-9-verdict49" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960217-9-verdict49" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960217-9-verdict49" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               GUILTY Of stealing the property
            </rs>, (Aged 30.) Both <rs id="t17960217-9-punish50" type="punishmentDescription">
